@startuml
actor Employee
participant "VTS System" as VTS
database DB

== Access VTS ==

Employee -> VTS : Open VTS via portal

alt Authentication failed
    VTS --> Employee : Show authentication error
else Authenticated
    VTS -> DB : Fetch requests & balances
    DB --> VTS : Return data
    VTS --> Employee : Display dashboard
end


== Select Request ==

Employee -> VTS : Select pending request
VTS --> Employee : Display editable form


== Modify Request ==

alt [Employee withdraws request]
    
    VTS --> Employee : Confirm withdrawal
    
    alt [Confirmed]
        VTS -> DB : Delete/Withdraw request
        VTS --> Employee : Return to home page
    else [Cancelled]
        VTS --> Employee : No changes made
    end

else [Employee edits request]
    
    loop Until valid input or cancel
        Employee -> VTS : Submit updated data
        VTS -> VTS : Validate changes

        opt [Error]
            VTS --> Employee : Show errors (highlight issues)
        end

        VTS -> DB : Update request
        VTS --> Employee : Return to home page
        break
    end

end

@enduml